	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm real interested in ordering a PowerPak, but from the <a href="http://www.retrousb.com/product_info.php?cPath=24&amp;products_id=34" class="postlink">product page</a>, I saw:
<br />
<br />"There may still be some sprite related graphics glitches on some NES systems."
<br />
<br />In which cases do the glitches occur?
<br />On which systems?
<br />
<br />
<br />Also, 
<br />how often does the mappers file get updated? 
<br />Is it pretty stable so far for most games?

		

		</td>
